Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.65,0:00:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.04,0:00:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.75,0:00:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.15,0:00:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.45,0:00:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.62,0:00:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.41,0:00:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.36,0:02:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝著傳說中的樂園——煌珠樂園進發的酷他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.07,0:02:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,發現了墜落的無人空賊艇 著手進行了修理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.53,0:02:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,與此同時出現了一個神秘的刺客意圖殺死酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.62,0:02:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍威也前所未有地被逼到絕境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.57,0:02:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,指使刺客的到底是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.35,0:02:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帶著疑問 酷他們繼續踏上了旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.23,0:03:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第八唱 令人戰慄的煌珠獵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.27,0:03:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷他們完成對空賊艇的修理後繼續航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是燃料的的補給卻是不可缺少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.44,0:03:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,偶然著陸的這個城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.25,0:03:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,意外的事件在等待著他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.87,0:03:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而這是凡夫俗子的他們所根本想不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.77,0:04:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,燃料補給和裝備就交給我這個內行人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.43,0:04:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.75,0:04:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼我們就去籌備食品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.48,0:04:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是留下一個人比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兩個人乘我們不在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.03,0:04:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又不是前輩你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我會揍人的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.63,0:04:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比起那些還是先吃飯 吃飯 吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.71,0:04:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.95,0:04:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 好 先找個地方填飽肚子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.17,0:04:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,輕鬆 輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.48,0:04:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼點事就吃不消的話就沒法帶蕾去煌珠樂園了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必須得變得更強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.11,0:04:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,強到能保護好蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.49,0:04:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.48,0:05:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.01,0:05:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.90,0:05:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我跟你是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.83,0:05:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是煌珠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,核石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫賽蕾娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.60,0:05:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正如蕾所說的是煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.08,0:05:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距這裏大概半天的路程有個村莊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那裏有個和我同契的同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.15,0:05:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然分開了很長時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但無論如何都想再見到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.48,0:05:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那又不需要逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.79,0:05:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.90,0:05:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.69,0:05:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過這身打扮走到這兒費了一番周折吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.64,0:06:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,與見不到他的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.50,0:06:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無聊到失魂落魄似的時間相比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.10,0:06:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這算不了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.99,0:06:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好勒 明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說是說 其實也不是很懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那先不提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.88,0:06:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,賽蕾娜 我們陪你一起去村裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.09,0:06:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾 行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.62,0:06:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.48,0:06:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.74,0:06:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.96,0:06:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.23,0:06:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,燃料罐難道就這麼放在外面不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快搬進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.42,0:06:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.45,0:06:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,賽蕾娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.91,0:06:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎麼會在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.28,0:06:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.92,0:06:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇雅 你認識的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被守護翼保護起來的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 為什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.47,0:07:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了 突然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.98,0:07:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們也是守護翼的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.70,0:07:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.77,0:07:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.85,0:07:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我絕對不回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,賽蕾娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從奇雅那裏聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.99,0:07:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該是被守護翼保護起來的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼會出現在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,逃出來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.96,0:07:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.44,0:07:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是在你的同意下接受守護翼的保護的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.10,0:07:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且聽說被保護的煌珠們很幸福地生活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.38,0:07:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸福？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.41,0:07:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奪走我幸福的正是守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.57,0:07:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.20,0:07:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,守護翼灌輸給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.00,0:07:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠和人類的歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.25,0:07:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生活在一起的話就會不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.17,0:07:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在守護翼的守護下生活會幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.65,0:07:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我離開了阿雷克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,確實在守護翼的庇護下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.67,0:08:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以舒舒服服地過日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.22,0:08:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是那裏沒有真正的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對於時間的流逝毫無概念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.19,0:08:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從世界中孤立出來的那個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.13,0:08:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對於我來說就像是牢籠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.89,0:08:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼那麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.08,0:08:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,守護翼是為你們煌珠考慮...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就別管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.23,0:08:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不會再回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.79,0:08:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我意識到我的幸福就是和那個人在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.73,0:08:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個人是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.09,0:08:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,賽蕾娜是去見自己的同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.57,0:08:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們沒有權利奪走我的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.14,0:08:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是想待在最愛的人的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.85,0:08:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,僅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.30,0:08:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,守護翼不會強行從你們那裏奪走什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.71,0:08:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,賽蕾娜在那裏哦 臥魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.68,0:09:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,臥魯真是過分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.75,0:09:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我都替你找到獵物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.16,0:09:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.30,0:09:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你只需默默地聽我的命令就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.00,0:09:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.98,0:09:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.02,0:09:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那傢伙是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,充滿殺氣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.91,0:09:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,賽蕾娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.82,0:09:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,賽蕾娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.72,0:09:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,狩獵的福音響起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.22,0:09:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會讓你溜走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.17,0:09:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.93,0:10:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道說那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.06,0:10:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷 把蕾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我 我撿到的飛船...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我撿到的寶貝...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.80,0:10:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.74,0:10:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是煌珠獵人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.68,0:10:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.35,0:10:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接受委託以捕獲煌珠為職業的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.68,0:10:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想要煌珠的人數不勝數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.59,0:10:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒守護翼什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.38,0:10:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.81,0:10:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也是同契者啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過小嘍囉就一邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.16,0:10:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.80,0:10:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然冒出來自以為是地亂說些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.48,0:11:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就是實力差距
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.98,0:11:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別想逃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.82,0:11:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裏不會讓你過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來會是一次很有趣的狩獵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.33,0:11:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,賽蕾娜就拜託酷你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.41,0:11:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.22,0:11:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.59,0:11:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿雷克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就快回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.74,0:11:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,賽蕾娜 等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.68,0:11:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我和守護翼無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是想遵守約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.37,0:12:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,約定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.73,0:12:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是說過嗎 陪你一起到村裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.64,0:12:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不想破壞約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.19,0:12:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這 這...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.87,0:12:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.88,0:12:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧 去村莊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.31,0:12:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.59,0:12:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,盾牌!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.18,0:12:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.18,0:12:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個獵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.39,0:12:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然和龍威不分上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很有一手嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.64,0:12:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.16,0:12:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夠了 住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個煌珠是打不過龍威他們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.83,0:12:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼啊 沒打過怎麼知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.77,0:12:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.98,0:12:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這傢伙只是衡量對手實力的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.14,0:13:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.93,0:13:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然把煌珠當東西一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.83,0:13:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哼 說得好聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,差不多該讓我過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.71,0:13:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.65,0:13:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幹什麼 有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.82,0:13:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 這裏...阿雷克斯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.29,0:13:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,家裏就我一個男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.64,0:14:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.41,0:14:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是我和阿雷克斯的房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.43,0:14:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是我半年前買的房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.37,0:14:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.68,0:14:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裏不是賽蕾娜你們的房子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.03,0:14:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會弄錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.85,0:14:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是為什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.82,0:14:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個時候的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.74,0:14:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都過去了這麼長時間了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.29,0:14:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,何時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.06,0:14:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,離開這裏是什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.59,0:14:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,賽蕾娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.76,0:14:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這不是賽蕾娜嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.78,0:14:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.11,0:15:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然是賽蕾娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是賽蕾娜的孫女吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.26,0:15:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好懷念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.89,0:15:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我小時候經常和她一起玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,花環我怎麼也做不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是賽蕾娜幫著做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.91,0:15:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,凱特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.95,0:15:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是凱特？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.93,0:15:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎麼知道我的名字的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.81,0:15:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 這樣啊 聽賽蕾娜說的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.01,0:15:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.43,0:15:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請問 這裏的阿雷克斯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.08,0:15:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再早點來就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大概一年之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.80,0:16:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,賽蕾娜離開之後都不知是過了幾十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.75,0:16:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即便如此 他還是一直獨自留在那房子裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.89,0:16:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或許是在等賽蕾娜回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.45,0:16:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠無法與人類度過同等的時光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.73,0:16:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠比人要活得更久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.49,0:16:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就因為那樣 這樣子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.73,0:16:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.59,0:16:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.07,0:16:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會再讓你逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.07,0:16:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們還沒死心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.50,0:16:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別想從我手中逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.73,0:16:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是沒有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.80,0:17:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.07,0:17:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接住的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.36,0:17:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒記性的廢物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.12,0:17:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能接住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.33,0:17:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該像流動的風一樣迴避過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像流動的風一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.12,0:17:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.55,0:17:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.70,0:17:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好看著對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.69,0:17:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,攻擊的時候肯定會露出破綻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.35,0:17:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.07,0:18:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.10,0:18:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次該我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.56,0:18:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.95,0:18:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於追上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.35,0:18:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,繼續剛才沒完的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,稍微等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呼吸還 還沒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.68,0:18:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.13,0:18:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還可以戰鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.33,0:18:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三對一 沒有勝算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.29,0:18:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.36,0:18:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們作為守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.50,0:18:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對於像你這樣的煌珠獵人就這麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,獵捕煌珠的獵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.23,0:18:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以保護為名一個接一個地關起來的守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.37,0:18:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我認為沒什麼不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.99,0:18:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.12,0:18:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.07,0:19:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一樣的 我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.28,0:19:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只希望你能幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個時候你對我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.74,0:19:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠和煌珠生活在一起最幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.50,0:20:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 儘管如此我還是想和你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想和你同生共死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.53,0:20:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.96,0:20:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把阿雷克斯和我的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.14,0:20:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,守護翼不存在的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.00,0:20:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們也就不用這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.93,0:20:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.37,0:20:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.11,0:20:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,賽蕾娜她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.19,0:20:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.23,0:20:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早上起來就不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.36,0:20:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不去找她沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.35,0:20:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒那必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.38,0:20:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且 我們的任務是把蕾帶到守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.35,0:20:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.75,0:20:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.96,0:20:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也可以那麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.23,0:20:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全是兩個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.49,0:21:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我和你們在一起很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.26,0:21:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別總是悶悶不樂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.75,0:21:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.68,0:21:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.88,0:21:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.70,0:21:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.77,0:22:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只能戰鬥的姐姐和只能看著的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.34,0:22:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黑暗之中邪惡在笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.23,0:23:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下回 港町的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.18,0:23:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第九唱 港町的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.05,0:23:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少女們有明天嗎

